#META# contentSummary: An acknowledgment of a sale of land by a family to a certain Maḥmūd b. ʿAlī for the price of 43 Mālikī gold *dīnārs*. The document is witnessed by 14 individuals and seems to be authenticated by a *qāḍī*, as indicated in the top margin.
